        Deprecated. 
        Try to execute the /httptest/smalltest.php over the provided net socket with a random id. Closes the socket after the test.
        Parameters:
        lowerLayerNetSocket - this net socket will be closed inside the method
        idPrefix - only digits and ASCII letters, becomes part of the id sent to the server
        timeoutInMs -
        Returns:
        true=test OK; false=test failed

        IOException
